Fullscreen API support

see
https://developer.mozilla.org/ru/docs/DOM/Using_fullscreen_mode

is strongly dependent on browser support
needs to be added to xs.env.Support

xs.dom.Element has `fullscreen` method

xs.fullscreen - singleton
xs.fullscreen#show(xs.dom.Element element)
xs.fullscreen#cancel()
xs.fullscreen#active - state
xs.fullscreen#element - xs.dom.Element reference


fullscreen
xs.fullscreen.event.Change              fullscreenchange    https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Events/fullscreenchange    An element was turned to fullscreen mode or back to normal mode.
xs.fullscreen.event.Error               fullscreenerror     https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/Events/fullscreenerror     It was impossible to switch to fullscreen mode for technical reasons or because the permission was denied.